{
  "texts": [
    "In alignment with the aim and research question posed in the current study, we enumerated hypotheses in alignment with the original UTAUT model, which are presented in Table 1 and Figure 1 (Venkatesh et al., 2003).",
    "Participants, who voluntarily agreed to participate in the research, were sampled from an English CEGEP in Canada (CEGEP, for a review, see Bazelais et al., 2016).",
    "Participants completed the questionnaire online.",
    "To ensure anonymity, students did not identify themselves.",
    "Additionally, no incentives and/or compensation was offered for participation."
  ]
}